拍到有警員在校園範圍徘徊，香港大學物業管理處控制中心其後指警員聲稱「僅為路過」。香港大學旋即於本日（7月17日）發表聲明斥警務人員違反既定守則，校方將作正式投訴。<br />\n<br />\n就此，校方向傳媒指，警方於校方作出投訴後，承認有西區分區警員巡邏時曾進入港大校園範圍，事後已與港大聯絡及解釋。警方續指就進入校園範圍有既定程序和指引，會嚴肅跟進，並保證同類事件不會再發生。<br />\n<br />\n而香港大學校長張翔教授於上周五和學生對話時曾經承諾，不會容許警察在沒有法律證明的情況下進入校園拘捕學生。<br />\n<br />\nSource :<a href=\"https://www.undergrad.hk/17676\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.undergrad.hk%2F17676&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQsqd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=764574c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.undergrad.hk/17676</a><br />\n正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：  繼續追究毅進仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新聞連結：<a href=\"https://www.undergrad.hk/17676\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.undergrad.hk%2F17676&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQsqd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=764574c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.undergrad.hk/17676</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:49:13.000Z","msg":"搞其他都未必理鳩你 KongU 出最撚多律師法官"},{"pid":"f21c1c7b8930c2ddbe056b1d3951a6042d1f693e","tid":1327632,"uid":20213,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:49:49.000Z","msg":"咪撚再標題黨啦屌"},{"pid":"2095502c0706c46219d64c8a559268c4cda37bc3","tid":1327632,"uid":210265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9b6a00c56db2ae9e863f6a683f72d322ae51295","tid":1327632,"uid":256067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:46:48.000Z","msg":"道歉就算？我屌毅進仔老母啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:52:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"764a2defdbba02c8d6328d2e1b491a76a3d6830c","tid":1327632,"uid":181035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:55:19.